[00:34.44] Hear me Doom-bringers
[00:39.81] Pale-bleak spawn of Hel
[00:45.03] Await the seething tide...
[00:58.03] 
[01:57.06] As a venomous omen
[02:02.25] An eagle pecks at the dead
[02:07.75] Its beak dripping blood...
[02:20.75] 
[02:13.41] At dusk death will dawn
[02:18.36] Denoument hoist the sail
[02:23.80] Skin and nail prevail...